Adds a basic e-commerce app

This commit adds a basic e-commerce Android app with frontend files (index.html, css/styles.css, js/*.js) and a Node.js backend server (server.js) using Replit's .replit configuration file.  The app includes product browsing, cart functionality, and simulated checkout.

